snippet.title: ATAK - Official Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1560140/ATAK
Join Discord: https://discord.gg/HedGryBQnD

ATAK is a real-time strategy action game with fast-paced battles and chaotic outcomes. Fight your way through the single-player campaign, challenge a friend in a custom battle or explore a multitude of minigames.
